((("This is the help screen. Press F2 to return to play. While playing you"))
 (("can click any object for help. Press PAUSE (or CONTROL-P) to pause,"))
 (("this makes it easier to click and see what all the different objects are."))
 ((""))
 (("You are the white square ") (nil :image "player") (" at the top left corner of"))
 (("the screen. You can move in any of the four orthogonal compass"))
 (("directions using the arrow keys, numeric keypad, or the letters"))
 (("H, J, K, and L. You cannot move diagonally, but some enemies can."))
 (("You are armed with a paint-absorbent hockey puck. The puck can"))
 (("pick up color from blocks and transfer it to other objects."))
 ((""))
 (("Press CONTROL-direction to fire the puck ") (nil :image "puck") (" in that direction. The"))
 (("current paint color is shown near the bottom of the screen along"))
 (("with the current level number and number of chevrons remaining."))

 (("Press ALT-direction to drop a 'chevron' ") 
  (nil :image "chevron-east") (" pointed in that direction."))
 (("Chevrons are arrows that change the direction of the puck"))
 (("and some enemies. You must find chevron refills on the ground, they"))
 (("look like the letter C. Each pickup gets you five chevrons,"))
 (("and you can hold a maximum of ten."))
 ((""))
 (("You cannot shoot enemies ") 
  (nil :image "tracer-east")
  (nil :image "monitor")
  (" instead, use chevrons to guide the enemies"))
 (("into the Black Holes: ") (nil :image "hole") (" The puck will be destroyed if it"))

 (("hits a red wire ") (nil :image "wire-east") (" or a black hole, so be careful where you fire."))
 (("You will also die instantly if you touch either a wire or a black"))
 (("hole, or are hit by any attack or projectile. When you die, the game"))
 (("is over, and you can press ESCAPE to start over at level 1, or"))
 (("CONTROL-Q to quit. Black holes can only be used once."))
 ((""))
 (("To get a new puck, pick up one of the pucks lying around: ") (nil :image "puckup"))
 (("Be careful, if you are already holding a puck, the one you pick up is wasted."))
 ((""))
 (("To clear a level, one must defeat all the enemies, and use the paint"))
