  (nil :image "brick-red")
  (nil :image "brick-yellow")
  (" ), which blocks"))
 (("the exit ( ") (nil :image "door") (" ) to the next level."))
 ((""))
 (("The game generates boards of increasing difficulty as you clear them,"))
